00:12:45,270 --> 00:12:46,390
Ke, are you implying

281
00:12:46,870 --> 00:12:47,960
that I should be somewhere else

282
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:49,670
by asking me that question?

283
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:51,790
That's right.

284
00:12:52,510 --> 00:12:54,080
Didn't he say
Third Young Master was inside?

285
00:12:56,270 --> 00:12:56,910
Grandmother,

286
00:12:57,390 --> 00:12:59,080
this is the Longevity Calligraphy
I wrote for you.

287
00:12:59,080 --> 00:13:00,200
I just finished framing it.

288
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:01,080
I'm here to deliver it to you.

289
00:13:01,790 --> 00:13:03,790
Good boy.

290
00:13:03,790 --> 00:13:05,360
But I saw Third Young Master

291
00:13:05,360 --> 00:13:06,320
entering the pavilion just now.

292
00:13:06,720 --> 00:13:08,550
If so, who's inside the pavilion?

293
00:13:08,550 --> 00:13:09,120
That's right.

294
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:09,750
Grandmother.

295
00:13:10,150 --> 00:13:10,840
Who is it?

296
00:13:11,790 --> 00:13:12,670
It's me.

297
00:13:17,720 --> 00:13:18,480
Bingyan?

298
00:13:19,360 --> 00:13:20,360
What are you doing here?

299
00:13:21,630 --> 00:13:23,240
I was together with Xiubo just now.

300
00:13:25,550 --> 00:13:26,670
Have you heard everything

301
00:13:26,670 --> 00:13:27,750
Ke Shizhao said just now?

302
00:13:28,150 --> 00:13:30,480
Bingyan, thank you for rescuing me
from the dark abyss.

303
00:13:40,240 --> 00:13:41,150
Tianlei...

304
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:46,440
What are you doing here?

305
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:50,030
Xiubo,

306
00:13:50,750 --> 00:13:51,840
I need to speak with you.

307
00:14:10,790 --> 00:14:11,630
Xiubo,

308
00:14:13,150 --> 00:14:14,360
we're both women.

309
00:14:15,080 --> 00:14:17,270
I understand your feelings for Tianlei.

310
00:14:20,320 --> 00:14:21,750
However, I'm in no way inferior

311
00:14:22,630 --> 00:14:23,960
to you.

312
00:14:25,600 --> 00:14:26,550
For us women,

313
00:14:27,360 --> 00:14:29,080
it's a fortunate thing for us

314
00:14:29,690 --> 00:14:31,810
to find a good husband
and spend our lives happily

315
00:14:32,740 --> 00:14:33,860
with them.

316
00:14:37,260 --> 00:14:37,890
However,

317
00:14:39,170 --> 00:14:40,380
the world is a vast place.

318
00:14:41,340 --> 00:14:42,460
Love and relationships

319
00:14:42,570 --> 00:14:44,460
shouldn't be the only things
a woman seeks in life.

320
00:14:45,620 --> 00:14:47,380
You should have your own goals in life.

321
00:14:49,380 --> 00:14:50,290
This way,

322
00:14:50,930 --> 00:14:52,260
you'll definitely find a man

323
00:14:52,500 --> 00:14:54,290
who suits you perfectly.

324
00:14:55,220 --> 00:14:56,980
He will dote on you and protect you.

325
00:15:04,570 --> 00:15:05,740
Don't do such

326
00:15:05,890 --> 00:15:07,170
silly things again.

327
00:15:09,650 --> 00:15:10,650
Bingyan.

328
00:15:13,890 --> 00:15:14,740
Silly girl.

329
00:15:18,620 --> 00:15:20,170
Why is Third Young Mistress
inside instead?

330
00:15:20,530 --> 00:15:22,810
And, why is she wearing
Third Young Master's outfit?

331
00:15:24,620 --> 00:15:25,650
Grandmother said

332
00:15:25,740 --> 00:15:27,020
I exhibited an air of heroism
when we played pitch pot last time.

333
00:15:27,140 --> 00:15:28,690
That's why I dressed myself
in Tianlei's outfit

334
00:15:28,930 --> 00:15:30,100
to make her happy.

335
00:15:32,500 --> 00:15:33,220
Good.

336
00:15:34,050 --> 00:15:34,740
Grandmother,

337
00:15:34,980 --> 00:15:37,620
Xiubo made some lotus fragrance for you.

338
00:15:37,770 --> 00:15:38,930
She used it on the Longevity Calligraphy.

339
00:15:38,930 --> 00:15:39,650
It has such a great fragrance.

340
00:15:43,340 --> 00:15:44,340
Come, Dear.

341
00:15:48,140 --> 00:15:53,340
[Longevity, Longevity Calligraphy]

342
00:16:11,340 --> 00:16:13,260
♪Dressed up for the big day♪

343
00:16:13,570 --> 00:16:14,380
Excellent!

344
00:16:15,650 --> 00:16:16,460
Grandmother.

345
00:16:16,860 --> 00:16:19,220
We wish you longevity!

346
00:16:19,650 --> 00:16:21,810
-Excellent!
-Excellent!

347
00:16:21,890 --> 00:16:22,570
Excellent!

348
00:16:23,220 --> 00:16:24,410
Same to you.

349
00:16:24,530 --> 00:16:26,170
-Congratulations.
-Congratulations, Old Madam.

350
00:16:26,380 --> 00:16:27,620
Congratulations, Old Madam.

351
00:16:28,100 --> 00:16:29,220
Good girl.

352
00:16:29,570 --> 00:16:31,980
Both of them are great girls.

353
00:16:34,620 --> 00:16:35,890
Excellent!

354
00:16:36,100 --> 00:16:37,100
-Excellent!
-Excellent!

355
00:16:37,410 --> 00:16:39,650
Same to you.

356
00:16:39,700 --> 00:16:42,300
♪We don't leave each other even in crisis♪

357
00:16:42,740 --> 00:16:46,780
♪Maybe for us this is just destiny♪

358
00:17:03,660 --> 00:17:05,660
♪Dressed up for the big day♪

359
00:17:05,900 --> 00:17:07,820
♪The sky is sunny and clear♪

360
00:17:09,180 --> 00:17:10,530
I'm tired. Let's take a break.

361
00:17:10,530 --> 00:17:11,130
Hurry.

362
00:17:11,220 --> 00:17:12,260
Pour Her Highness some tea.

363
00:17:12,460 --> 00:17:14,380
♪By weird accidents we meet♪

364
00:17:14,620 --> 00:17:16,660
♪Even across a thousand li♪

365
00:17:17,090 --> 00:17:17,770
Your Highness.

366
00:17:19,090 --> 00:17:19,770
What's the matter?

367
00:17:20,330 --> 00:17:22,500
Did Father say I have to get married?

368
00:17:22,850 --> 00:17:24,290
Your Highness,
this is a joyous occasion for you.

369
00:17:24,290 --> 00:17:25,500
This time, His Majesty has arranged

370
00:17:25,500 --> 00:17:27,260
Marquis of the North, General Yuan Buqu,
to be your consort.

371
00:17:27,460 --> 00:17:29,810
Your Highness is truly fortunate.

372
00:17:30,900 --> 00:17:32,260
I don't know if he's a good guy for me

373
00:17:32,260 --> 00:17:33,260
or not.

374
00:17:34,460 --> 00:17:34,980
Eunuch,

375
00:17:34,980 --> 00:17:36,130
I have to see him for myself
to assess him.

376
00:17:36,420 --> 00:17:38,530
All those portraits you showed me before

377
00:17:38,530 --> 00:17:39,610
were fake.

378
00:17:40,260 --> 00:17:40,980
Your Highness,

379
00:17:41,220 --> 00:17:43,220
I know not many men

380
00:17:43,220 --> 00:17:44,330
had caught your eye.

381
00:17:45,260 --> 00:17:46,570
However, Consort Yuan is...

382
00:17:47,290 --> 00:17:48,330
I haven't agreed to it yet.

383
00:17:48,420 --> 00:17:49,900
I have to see him for myself.

384
00:17:50,090 --> 00:17:51,180
I need to see

385
00:17:51,330 --> 00:17:53,500
if he's deformed

386
00:17:53,500 --> 00:17:54,900
or ugly.

387
00:17:58,530 --> 00:18:00,700
I thought the best scholar
of the Ministry of Personnel

388
00:18:00,700 --> 00:18:02,220
was bent on marrying me?

389
00:18:02,220 --> 00:18:03,220
That's right.

390
00:18:04,810 --> 00:18:07,090
I've read the poems and verses

391
00:18:07,090 --> 00:18:08,370
he wrote for me to you guys before.

392
00:18:09,290 --> 00:18:10,330
It was so touching.

393
00:18:10,900 --> 00:18:11,700
Touching?

394
00:18:12,330 --> 00:18:13,900
He was just stringing together
ornate phrases

395
00:18:14,290 --> 00:18:15,570
to express his fake feelings for me.

396
00:18:15,980 --> 00:18:17,050
What a terrible guy.

397
00:18:17,500 --> 00:18:18,290
He even said

398
00:18:18,290 --> 00:18:20,330
that he could go through dangers

399
00:18:20,770 --> 00:18:22,130
and do anything for my sake.

400
00:18:22,130 --> 00:18:23,370
Would you guys even believe that?

401
00:18:23,570 --> 00:18:24,260
We would.

402
00:18:26,460 --> 00:18:27,260
You too?

403
00:18:27,770 --> 00:18:28,570
Yes.

404
00:18:29,130 --> 00:18:31,020
Anyway, I don't believe him.

405
00:18:31,090 --> 00:18:31,770
Your Highness.

406
00:18:32,810 --> 00:18:34,500
Your Highness,
the arrow you requested is ready.

407
00:18:45,980 --> 00:18:46,530
Eunuch,

408
00:18:46,810 --> 00:18:48,050
why don't we play a new game?

409
00:18:52,090 --> 00:18:53,610
Your Majesty,

410
00:18:54,050 --> 00:18:55,570
Consort Yuan Buqu has sent his men here

411
00:18:55,850 --> 00:18:57,420
to deliver a memorial to His Majesty.

412
00:18:57,810 --> 00:18:59,700
His Majesty requests you to read it.

413
00:19:00,050 --> 00:19:00,700
Read it.

414
00:19:01,090 --> 00:19:01,740
Yes, Your Majesty.

415
00:19:02,740 --> 00:19:04,460
Your Majesty, thank you for your grace.

416
00:19:05,050 --> 00:19:07,460
I, Yuan Buqu, was rushing to the capital
after receiving the imperial edict.

417
00:19:07,900 --> 00:19:09,810
I was passing the land of Qilu.

418
00:19:10,020 --> 00:19:11,980
I have to pay respect to my ancestors
in my hometown.

419
00:19:12,370 --> 00:19:13,980
Your Majesty, please allow me

420
00:19:14,130 --> 00:19:17,050
to pay respect to my ancestors
before returning to the capital

421
00:19:17,330 --> 00:19:18,850
so that I can fulfill my filial duties.

422
00:19:19,370 --> 00:19:21,770
Spiritual Mountain is a place endowed with

423
00:19:22,020 --> 00:19:23,500
the fine spirits of the universe.

424
00:19:23,700 --> 00:19:26,220
Your Majesty, please allow Her Highness

425
00:19:26,370 --> 00:19:30,700
to join me in visiting Spiritual Mountain.

426
00:19:30,700 --> 00:19:31,900
[Fifth year of Xianqing, early August.]

427
00:19:31,900 --> 00:19:33,020
Yuan Buqu

428
00:19:33,180 --> 00:19:35,050
is quite a filial child.

429
00:19:36,610 --> 00:19:37,740
Prioritizing filial piety

430
00:19:38,090 --> 00:19:39,260
and one's relationships, huh?

431
00:19:40,370 --> 00:19:41,020
Not bad at all.

432
00:19:41,130 --> 00:19:42,220
Your Majesty,

433
00:19:42,530 --> 00:19:45,850
your discerning eyes could
truly tell greatness from mediocrity.

434
00:19:46,050 --> 00:19:50,130
You've found an excellent consort
for Her Highness.

435
00:19:51,610 --> 00:19:53,900
Changping is proud and aloof.

436
00:19:54,460 --> 00:19:56,850
We still don't know
what kind of trouble she'll stir up.

437
00:19:59,130 --> 00:20:00,500
Although I'm the empress

438
00:20:01,020 --> 00:20:02,290
and the female head of the nation,

439
00:20:03,130 --> 00:20:05,020
I cannot select
a consort for the princess.

440
00:20:06,980 --> 00:20:07,610
Is this what they meant by

441
00:20:08,090 --> 00:20:09,770
"Do not do others what you would not

442
00:20:10,530 --> 00:20:11,900
have them do to you?"

443
00:20:13,130 --> 00:20:14,020
Greetings, Your Highness.

444
00:20:14,460 --> 00:20:15,700
Spare the formalities. Have a seat.

445
00:20:28,090 --> 00:20:28,980
Your Highness, I prefer

446
00:20:29,130 --> 00:20:30,610
standing up.

447
00:20:35,330 --> 00:20:36,700
By the way, top scorer,

448
00:20:36,940 --> 00:20:37,940
do you remember

449
00:20:38,090 --> 00:20:39,900
the poems and verses you wrote for me?

450
00:20:40,020 --> 00:20:41,130
They're imprinted in my heart.

451
00:20:42,130 --> 00:20:43,810
Your Highness,
I've admired you for a long time.

452
00:20:44,090 --> 00:20:45,980
Your Highness is
the most beautiful lady in the world.

453
00:20:46,330 --> 00:20:47,260
Many people

454
00:20:47,460 --> 00:20:49,460
have fallen to your charm.

455
00:20:50,770 --> 00:20:51,570
Is there anything else?

456
00:20:54,610 --> 00:20:55,610
Your Highness,

457
00:20:56,220 --> 00:20:58,850
I think about you day and night.

458
00:20:59,020 --> 00:21:01,370
I'm willing to go through dangers
and do anything for your sake.

459
00:21:03,810 --> 00:21:05,220
If that's the case,

460
00:21:05,900 --> 00:21:07,850
does that mean you'll do anything

461
00:21:08,090 --> 00:21:09,130
I tell you to do?

462
00:21:09,460 --> 00:21:10,610
Yes, Your Highness.

463
00:21:10,740 --> 00:21:11,610
I will even go through

464
00:21:11,740 --> 00:21:13,020
fire and flames for you
as long as you say the word,

465
00:21:13,020 --> 00:21:14,290
Your Highness.

466
00:21:14,570 --> 00:21:15,130
Good.

467
00:21:16,130 --> 00:21:17,220
Your Highness,

468
00:21:17,370 --> 00:21:19,370
even if you order me
to acquire the moon for you,

469
00:21:19,530 --> 00:21:21,090
I shall search
the entire world for a ladder

470
00:21:21,090 --> 00:21:22,530
that can reach the heavens itself
to acquire it for you.

471
00:21:22,530 --> 00:21:23,530
Great.

472
00:21:23,610 --> 00:21:24,610
If that's the case,

473
00:21:24,610 --> 00:21:26,530
I'll give you another chance today.

474
00:21:47,130 --> 00:21:50,050
I'll draw a small circle here.

475
00:21:53,050 --> 00:21:53,740
And,

476
00:21:54,090 --> 00:21:56,610
you have to stay inside the circle.

477
00:21:56,740 --> 00:21:57,610
Can you do that?

478
00:21:58,330 --> 00:21:59,260
That's easy.

479
00:21:59,530 --> 00:22:00,570
I will never move,

480
00:22:00,850 --> 00:22:01,740
even if lightning strikes me down.

481
00:22:03,050 --> 00:22:03,770
It's a deal, then.

482
00:22:03,770 --> 00:22:04,770
I'm a man of my word.

483
00:22:05,330 --> 00:22:05,900
All right.

484
00:22:06,570 --> 00:22:07,130
Eunuch.

485
00:22:10,020 --> 00:22:11,850
Put this apple on your head.

486
00:22:26,850 --> 00:22:27,610
Your Highness,

487
00:22:27,810 --> 00:22:29,460
please don't do this.

488
00:22:30,050 --> 00:22:31,700
Arrows cannot discern
human beings from apples!

489
00:22:31,700 --> 00:22:32,330
Your Highness!

490
00:22:33,850 --> 00:22:35,460
Can you stop moving around?

491
00:22:35,460 --> 00:22:36,500
You already left the circle.

492
00:22:37,810 --> 00:22:38,530
I won't move.

493
00:22:38,530 --> 00:22:40,850
Can we change the rule of the game then?

494
00:22:43,850 --> 00:22:44,500
Oh yeah.

495
00:22:45,130 --> 00:22:46,700
I forgot to tell you

496
00:22:47,050 --> 00:22:49,130
that I was bad at archery.

497
00:22:49,370 --> 00:22:49,980
However,

498
00:22:49,980 --> 00:22:50,850
I will do my best.

499
00:22:53,700 --> 00:22:54,370
Don't do this!

500
00:22:54,370 --> 00:22:54,980
Your Highness!

501
00:22:54,980 --> 00:22:56,220
You mustn't do this!

502
00:22:57,050 --> 00:22:58,370
Eunuch, can you shut up?

503
00:22:58,370 --> 00:22:59,500
What if I hurt you by accident?

504
00:22:59,700 --> 00:23:00,370
Your Highness,

505
00:23:00,370 --> 00:23:02,180
you mustn't joke around with this!

506
00:23:02,660 --> 00:23:03,290
Get out of my way.

507
00:23:05,740 --> 00:23:07,900
Your Highness!

508
00:23:08,370 --> 00:23:08,940
Please don't do this!

509
00:23:09,900 --> 00:23:10,530
Your Highness!

510
00:23:12,020 --> 00:23:13,090
Your Highness! Please don't do this!

511
00:23:14,980 --> 00:23:15,570
Your Highness!

512
00:23:16,260 --> 00:23:18,810
Please don't do this!

513
00:23:22,020 --> 00:23:22,700
Please don't do this!

514
00:23:35,370 --> 00:23:37,260
Your Highness, thank you for sparing me.

515
00:23:48,180 --> 00:23:50,370
Your Highness, you...

516
00:23:55,220 --> 00:23:55,980
Stop pretending.

517
00:23:56,220 --> 00:23:58,050
The tip of the arrow was made from wax.

518
00:24:03,020 --> 00:24:04,290
What a coward.

519
00:24:04,420 --> 00:24:05,050
Look at you.

520
00:24:05,260 --> 00:24:06,290
You have no courage whatsoever.

521
00:24:06,290 --> 00:24:07,740
You want to go through
fire and flames for me?

522
00:24:07,740 --> 00:24:08,290
As if.

523
00:24:08,290 --> 00:24:08,940
Leave immediately.

524
00:24:08,940 --> 00:24:09,500
Yes, Your Highness.

525
00:24:09,500 --> 00:24:11,810
[Her Majesty has arrived.]

526
00:24:11,810 --> 00:24:12,570
Eunuch!

527
00:24:12,570 --> 00:24:14,130
No outsiders are supposed to be here!

528
00:24:14,130 --> 00:24:16,260
We'll be in trouble
if Her Majesty finds out!

529
00:24:16,260 --> 00:24:17,610
Hurry! Follow me out of the palace!

530
00:24:17,610 --> 00:24:18,220
The apple!

531
00:24:18,220 --> 00:24:18,980
Hurry!

532
00:24:24,220 --> 00:24:27,740
[Her Majesty has arrived.]

533
00:24:31,770 --> 00:24:33,530
Greetings, Mother.

534
00:24:34,740 --> 00:24:35,420
You may rise.

535
00:24:36,420 --> 00:24:37,570
What were you laughing at?

536
00:24:37,900 --> 00:24:39,220
I could hear you all the way back there.

537
00:24:39,220 --> 00:24:40,130
Mother, please have a seat.

538
00:24:41,460 --> 00:24:42,660
Just now,

539
00:24:42,850 --> 00:24:43,700
we were practicing archery

540
00:24:44,020 --> 00:24:44,660
and

541
00:24:45,500 --> 00:24:46,420
skipping ropes together.

542
00:24:49,500 --> 00:24:51,090
You will be married soon, you know?

543
00:24:51,370 --> 00:24:52,610
Having fun shouldn't be
the only thing on your mind now.

544
00:24:54,330 --> 00:24:55,420
Your consort has written to us.

545
00:24:57,570 --> 00:24:58,290
Mother,

546
00:24:58,700 --> 00:25:00,810
I don't even know
what Yuan Buqu looks like.

547
00:25:00,810 --> 00:25:02,020
How could I get married to him?

548
00:25:03,220 --> 00:25:04,290
In his letter, he wrote

549
00:25:05,090 --> 00:25:07,130
that he wished to invite you
to Spiritual Mountain

550
00:25:08,330 --> 00:25:09,980
to enjoy the sunrise

551
00:25:10,460 --> 00:25:11,980
and the excellent view there.

552
00:25:13,610 --> 00:25:15,050
I didn't know

553
00:25:15,660 --> 00:25:17,500
if you wanted to go there or not.

554
00:25:18,460 --> 00:25:19,980
Mother, I want to go there.

555
00:25:20,810 --> 00:25:22,050
It's boring to stay in the imperial garden

556
00:25:22,050 --> 00:25:23,130
every day.

557
00:25:23,130 --> 00:25:24,130
When are we leaving?

558
00:25:24,130 --> 00:25:25,370
Look at how impatient you are.

559
00:25:27,460 --> 00:25:29,660
Let's forget about
when you'll depart for now.

560
00:25:30,700 --> 00:25:31,980
I have three conditions.

561
00:25:32,220 --> 00:25:33,460
You have to agree to it before you can go.

562
00:25:33,900 --> 00:25:34,770
Mother, go ahead.

563
00:25:36,260 --> 00:25:37,130
First,

564
00:25:38,130 --> 00:25:40,850
