580
00:26:15,700 --> 00:26:17,180
All right. I agree.

581
00:26:17,900 --> 00:26:18,900
You're not allowed to throw a tantrum

582
00:26:19,460 --> 00:26:21,530
on your way there.

583
00:26:22,420 --> 00:26:23,330
For the third condition,

584
00:26:23,770 --> 00:26:26,530
