to take care of her.

593
00:26:42,260 --> 00:26:43,810
Please don't worry.

594
00:26:45,020 --> 00:26:45,660
Mother,

595
00:26:46,220 --> 00:26:47,740
since I've already agreed
to all three of your conditions,

