599
00:26:56,370 --> 00:26:57,500
Firstly,

600
00:26:57,940 --> 00:26:59,610
I will select my consort

601
00:26:59,610 --> 00:27:00,900
myself.

602
00:27:02,500 --> 00:27:04,330
