arranged the marriage for you.

605
00:27:10,260 --> 00:27:11,530
The emperor's words
are to be taken seriously.

606
00:27:13,500 --> 00:27:15,570
If that's the case,
I'll jump down from Spiritual Mountain!

607
00:27:15,660 --> 00:27:16,220
You!

608
00:27:16,850 --> 00:27:17,530
Your Highness,

609
00:27:17,940 --> 00:27:19,020
