610
00:27:19,220 --> 00:27:20,330
Please calm down.

611
00:27:22,420 --> 00:27:23,220
What about this?

612
00:27:24,420 --> 00:27:26,370
You can head to Spiritual Mountain and see

613
00:27:26,370 --> 00:27:27,370
the kind of person Yuan Buqu is for now.

614
00:27:28,130 --> 00:27:28,900
We can discuss

615
00:27:30,220 --> 00:27:31,530
the details after your return.

616
00:27:33,020 --> 00:27:34,420
All right. Mother, you're the best.

617
00:27:38,420 --> 00:27:40,260
Here's the second condition.

618
00:27:41,020 --> 00:27:42,500
Secondly, they can only

619
