00:28:10,900 --> 00:28:11,740
About that...

633
00:28:13,500 --> 00:28:15,500
Your plan is pretty thorough.

634
00:28:17,330 --> 00:28:18,020
All right then.

635
00:28:18,700 --> 00:28:20,220
It's fine as long as
you don't cause trouble for me.

636
00:28:20,580 --> 00:28:23,620
[Qi Residence]

637
00:28:25,180 --> 00:28:26,460
I'm here to bid farewell.

638
00:28:26,770 --> 00:28:28,980
Bingyan, thank you for making me
realize my foolishness.

