00:28:28,980 --> 00:28:31,370
That's how I was able to see through
Ke Shizhao's devious plans

640
00:28:31,660 --> 00:28:32,980
and avoid committing a huge mistake.

641
00:28:33,700 --> 00:28:34,660
Xiubo,

642
00:28:34,850 --> 00:28:36,370
you must love yourself

643
00:28:36,370 --> 00:28:37,980
and find a man who loves you.

644
00:28:39,850 --> 00:28:41,180
I grew up together

645
