with Tianlei since young.

646
00:28:44,090 --> 00:28:45,530
Back then, I thought

647
00:28:45,850 --> 00:28:47,370
marriage was the most important thing

648
00:28:47,530 --> 00:28:48,740
for a girl.

649
00:28:49,020 --> 00:28:49,740
I thought

650
00:28:49,740 --> 00:28:51,900
Tianlei was my best choice.

651
00:28:52,530 --> 00:28:53,850
But Bingyan,

652
