left behind by Grandmother.

667
00:29:27,980 --> 00:29:29,660
Xiubo, your heart and spirit are pure.

668
00:29:29,940 --> 00:29:32,180
I'm sure you can manage
the business successfully.

669
00:29:32,570 --> 00:29:33,850
Tianlei, you flatter me.

670
00:29:35,810 --> 00:29:36,610
However,

671
00:29:37,570 --> 00:29:40,370
Ke Shizhao is bent on
getting rid of you guys.

672
00:29:40,900 --> 00:29:42,900
