when you put them together.

682
00:30:14,180 --> 00:30:16,850
Bingyan, I shall give this to you.

683
00:30:17,130 --> 00:30:18,660
I hope that you two

684
00:30:19,180 --> 00:30:20,460
can grow old together.

685
00:30:36,050 --> 00:30:36,900
Thank you, Xiubo.

686
00:30:37,850 --> 00:30:38,740
I shall take my leave.

687
00:30:45,130 --> 00:30:45,740
Take care.

