Dear,

704
00:33:46,460 --> 00:33:47,260
you're pretty good at martial arts.

705
00:33:51,260 --> 00:33:52,020
I'll leave the rest

706
00:33:52,940 --> 00:33:53,770
to you.

707
00:34:08,780 --> 00:34:09,300
I'll break your legs

708
00:34:09,300 --> 00:34:10,250
