709
00:34:10,340 --> 00:34:11,250
Who exactly are you?

710
00:34:11,860 --> 00:34:13,050
I'm in pain!

711
00:34:14,900 --> 00:34:17,090
Heroine, please spare me!

712
00:34:18,530 --> 00:34:20,650
I...

713
00:34:20,650 --> 00:34:23,050
I don't even know who I am now!

714
00:34:23,500 --> 00:34:25,500
Please forget about me!

715
00:34:25,570 --> 00:34:26,500
I can't fight well!

716
00:34:26,500 --> 00:34:28,610
I was never your match to begin with!

717
00:34:29,170 --> 00:34:30,090
At least you know what's good for you.

718
00:34:32,860 --> 00:34:33,530
Heroine,

719
00:34:35,530 --> 00:34:37,650
may I know your name?

720
00:34:37,980 --> 00:34:40,170
At least I won't die in ignorance.

721
00:34:41,610 --> 00:34:43,780
I have nothing to hide.

722
00:34:43,980 --> 00:34:45,210
I'm Li Yuhu from Yangzhou.

723
00:35:22,820 --> 00:35:23,420
Young Master,

724
00:35:24,860 --> 00:35:25,690
we're in trouble.

725
00:35:26,210 --> 00:35:27,650
Third Young Mistress
is an expert martial artist.

726
00:35:27,650 --> 00:35:28,860
She's extraordinary.

727
00:35:28,860 --> 00:35:29,860
My men

728
00:35:29,860 --> 00:35:31,090
were no match for her.

729
00:35:31,690 --> 00:35:34,500
Third Young Master wasn't sick at all.

730
00:35:34,650 --> 00:35:35,820
He was swinging his sword with ease.

731
00:35:35,980 --> 00:35:36,980
He punched me in the face

732
00:35:37,170 --> 00:35:38,460
