Are you serious?

741
00:35:58,050 --> 00:35:58,690
Yes.

742
00:35:59,210 --> 00:35:59,690
Young Master,

743
00:36:00,860 --> 00:36:02,900
I'm afraid it's no easy feat

744
00:36:02,900 --> 00:36:04,380
