745
00:36:04,820 --> 00:36:05,690
My men

746
00:36:05,690 --> 00:36:06,900
were no match for them.

747
00:36:07,130 --> 00:36:07,860
Moreover,

748
00:36:08,170 --> 00:36:10,130
we failed to get them this time.

749
00:36:10,380 --> 00:36:11,500
I'm afraid it'll be more difficult

750
00:36:11,610 --> 00:36:13,210
