751
00:36:13,530 --> 00:36:14,170
Useless fool.

752
00:36:16,500 --> 00:36:17,170
Wait.

753
00:36:19,130 --> 00:36:20,460
Why would the daughter of the Du family

754
00:36:22,170 --> 00:36:23,380
