774
00:36:58,900 --> 00:37:00,820
"I have nothing to hide.

775
00:37:00,820 --> 00:37:02,210
I'm Li Yuhu from Yangzhou."

776
00:37:08,340 --> 00:37:09,340
Li Yuhu?

777
00:37:09,940 --> 00:37:11,020
Are you sure you heard that?

778
00:37:11,610 --> 00:37:13,090
Of course.

779
00:37:16,210 --> 00:37:17,380
